OL,3,CDiddy 'truly sorry' after footage of
OL,4,Cattack on ex-girlfriend in hotel
OL,6,FSean "Diddy" Combs has said he is
OL,7,F"truly sorry" after footage from 2016
OL,8,Fappears to show him attacking his then-
OL,9,Fgirlfriend in a Los Angeles hotel
OL,10,Fhallway.
OL,12,FThe video, aired by CNN on Friday,
OL,13,Ftowards R&B singer Cassandra "Cassie"
OL,14,FVentura.
OL,16,FThe security footage shows a man in a
OL,17,Fwhite towel, running down a hotel
OL,18,Fcorridor before grabbing a woman by
OL,19,Fthe back of her neck, throwing her to
OL,20,Fthe ground and kicking her.
