OL,3,CDiddy 'truly sorry' after footage of
OL,4,Cattack on ex-girlfriend in hotel
OL,6,FIn a statement posted on social media,
OL,7,FMr Combs said: "I take full
OL,8,Fresponsibility for my actions in that
OL,9,Fvideo. I was disgusted then when I did
OL,10,Fit. I'm disgusted now.
OL,12,F"It's so difficult to reflect on the
OL,13,Fdarkest times in your life, but
OL,14,Fsometimes you got to do that."
OL,16,FHe adds: "I went and I sought out
OL,17,Fprofessional help. I got into going to
OL,18,Ftherapy, going to rehab.
