OL,6,F"I had to ask God for his mercy and
OL,7,Fgrace. I'm so sorry. But I'm committed
OL,8,Fto be a better man each and every day.
OL,9,FI'm not asking for forgiveness. I'm
OL,10,Ftruly sorry."
OL,12,FMs Ventura settled a law suit against
OL,13,FMr Combs in November over what she
OL,14,Fsaid was years of sexual, physical and
OL,15,Femotional abuse.
OL,17,FThe rapper and producer faces other
OL,18,Fallegations of physical and sexual
OL,19,Fviolence from multiple people ` all of
OL,20,Fwhich he denies.
