OL,6,FThe security camera video, dated March
OL,7,F5, 2016, closely resembles the
OL,8,Fdescription of an incident at an
OL,9,FInterContinental Hotel in the Century
OL,10,FCity area of Los Angeles described in
OL,11,FMs Ventura's lawsuit.
OL,13,FThe suit alleges that Mr Combs paid
OL,14,Fthe hotel $50,000 for the security
OL,15,Fvideo immediately after the incident.
OL,16,FNeither he or his representatives have
OL,17,Faddressed that specific allegation.
OL,19,FCNN did not say how it obtained the
OL,20,Ffootage.
